OL,3,CPope in critical condition with early
OL,4,Ckidney failure, says Vatican
OL,6,FThe 88-year-old remains "critical" and
OL,7,Fhas been monitored closely by doctors
OL,8,Ffor more than a week, as ITV News'
OL,9,FEllie Pitt reports from Rome
OL,11,FPope Francis remains in a critical
OL,12,Fcondition with blood tests showing
OL,13,Fmild signs of kidney failure "which is
OL,14,Fcurrently under control," the Vatican
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FHe has not shown further respiratory
OL,18,Fcrises since Saturday when he suffered
OL,19,Fa prolonged asthmatic respiratory
OL,20,Fcrisis while being treated for
OL,21,Fpneumonia and a complex lung infection.
