OL,6,FSome of his blood tests indicate "an
OL,7,Finitial, mild, renal failure, which is
OL,8,Fcurrently under control," the Vatican
OL,9,Fsaid, adding that the Pope continues
OL,10,Fto be "vigilant and well-oriented."
OL,12,FEarlier on Sunday, the Holy Father
OL,13,Fasked well-wishers to "pray for me,"
OL,14,Fas he said in a statement: "In recent
OL,15,Fdays, I have received many messages of
OL,16,Faffection, and I have been
OL,17,Fparticularly struck by the letters and
OL,18,Fdrawings from children.
