OL,6,F"Thank you for this closeness, and for
OL,7,Fthe prayers of comfort I have received
OL,8,Ffrom all over the world! I entrust you
OL,9,Fall to the intercession of Mary, and I
OL,10,Fask you to pray for me."
OL,12,FThe Vatican confirmed on Sunday
OL,13,Fmorning that the Pope had a "peaceful
OL,14,Fnight" and was resting following a
OL,15,Frespiratory crisis and blood
OL,16,Ftransfusions.
OL,18,FVatican spokesman Matteo Bruni's one-
OL,19,Fline statement didn't mention if
OL,20,FFrancis was up or eating breakfast.
