OL,3,CPope in critical condition with early
OL,4,Ckidney failure, says Vatican
OL,6,FThe brief update came after doctors
OL,7,Fsaid the 88-year-old pope, who had
OL,8,Fpart of one lung removed as a young
OL,9,Fman, was in critical condition.
OL,11,FThe Pope has been in hospital for over
OL,12,Fa week, and will once again miss the
OL,13,Ftraditional Angelus prayer for the
OL,14,Fsecond Sunday in a row.
OL,16,FThe pope received "high flows" of
OL,17,Foxygen to help him breathe. He also
OL,18,Freceived blood transfusions after
OL,19,Ftests showed low counts of platelets,
OL,20,Fwhich are needed for clotting, the
OL,21,FVatican said in a late update.
